<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/126529-people-are-saying-this-series-is-quite">People are saying this series is quite different from others they&#39;ve read in the fantasy or dystopia genres. Is it at all predictable? How do you think the second book in the Kyrennei series will open? What do you think the characters will do?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_126529'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F22919146-the-soul-and-the-seed">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/126529-people-are-saying-this-series-is-quite">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/126529-people-are-saying-this-series-is-quite">Add your answer</a>
</li>
